     A*================================================================
     A* POKEBATTL - Pokemon Battle Display File
     A* 27x132 for Mocha 5250
     A*
     A* Layout:
     A*   Rows  1-12  OPPONENT  info cols 5-40   art cols 91-130 (40w x 12h)
     A*   Rows 13-24  PLAYER    art cols 5-44    info cols 91-123 (40w x 12h)
     A*   Rows 25-27  MSG / MOVEMENU / SWITCHMN
     A*
     A* Color indicators (set by POKEBATTLE before WRITE):
     A*   Player side (PLART*):  30=GRN 31=WHT 32=RED 33=TRQ 34=YLW 35=PNK 36=BLU
     A*   Opponent side (OPART*): 40=GRN 41=WHT 42=RED 43=TRQ 44=YLW 45=PNK 46=BLU
     A*   Only one indicator per side should be on at a time.
     A*================================================================
     A                                      DSPSIZ(27 132)
     A                                      CA03(03 'F3=Exit')
     A*
     A*== HEADER - Empty format, writing it clears the screen =====
     A          R HEADER
     A*
     A*== OPPONENT - Rows 1-12 ====================================
     A*  Info on LEFT (cols 5-40), art on RIGHT (cols 91-130)
     A          R OPPONENT
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A                                      PUTOVR
     A                                      CLRL(*NO)
     A                                      FRCDTA
     A                                  1  5'POKE400'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A            ROOMCD         8A  O  1 14
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            BMODE          2A  O  1 24
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A                                  2  5'Enemy:'
     A            OPNAME        12A  O  2 12
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            OPLVL          5A  O  2 25
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            OPTYPE        23A  O  3  5
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A                                  4  5'HP:'
     A            OPHPBR        20A  O  4  9
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            OPCRHP         3S 0O  4 31
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A                                  4 34'/'
     A            OPMXHP         3S 0O  4 35
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            OPSTAT        10A  O  5  5
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            OPART1        40A  O  1 91
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A  40                                  COLOR(GRN)
     A  41                                  COLOR(WHT)
     A  42                                  COLOR(RED)
     A  43                                  COLOR(TRQ)
     A  44                                  COLOR(YLW)
     A  45                                  COLOR(PNK)
     A  46                                  COLOR(BLU)
     A            OPART2        40A  O  2 91
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A  40                                  COLOR(GRN)
     A  41                                  COLOR(WHT)
     A  42                                  COLOR(RED)
     A  43                                  COLOR(TRQ)
     A  44                                  COLOR(YLW)
     A  45                                  COLOR(PNK)
     A  46                                  COLOR(BLU)
