     A*
     A*== MSGLINE - Narration (WRITE + PUTOVR) ====================
     A          R MSGLINE
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A                                      PUTOVR
     A                                      CLRL(*NO)
     A                                      FRCDTA
     A                                      ERASE(MOVEMENU)
     A                                      ERASE(SWITCHMN)
     A            MSG1          70A  O 25  5
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            MSG2          70A  O 26  5
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A            MSG3          70A  O 27  5
     A                                      OVRDTA
     A*
     A*== MOVEMENU - Move selection (EXFMT) =======================
     A          R MOVEMENU
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A                                      ERASE(MSGLINE)
     A                                 25  5'What will you do?'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A            MV1NAM        16A  O 26  5
     A            MV1PP          7A  O 26 23
     A            MV2NAM        16A  O 26 35
     A            MV2PP          7A  O 26 53
     A            MV3NAM        16A  O 27  5
     A            MV3PP          7A  O 27 23
     A            MV4NAM        16A  O 27 35
     A            MV4PP          7A  O 27 53
     A            MVSEL          1A  B 26 70
     A                                 26 73'(1-4)'
     A*
     A*== SWITCHMN - Switch Pokemon (EXFMT) =======================
     A          R SWITCHMN
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A                                      ERASE(MSGLINE)
     A                                 25  5'Choose a Pokemon:'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A            SW1NAM        12A  O 26  5
     A            SW1HP          7A  O 26 19
     A            SW2NAM        12A  O 26 30
     A            SW2HP          7A  O 26 44
     A            SW3NAM        12A  O 26 55
     A            SW3HP          7A  O 26 69
     A            SW4NAM        12A  O 27  5
     A            SW4HP          7A  O 27 19
     A            SW5NAM        12A  O 27 30
     A            SW5HP          7A  O 27 44
     A            SW6NAM        12A  O 27 55
     A            SW6HP          7A  O 27 69
     A            SWSEL          1A  B 26 80
     A                                 26 83'(1-6)'
